name: An Cuby Adventure
description:
Welcome to the most... cubical adventure there is?
  • In this world, your objective is to defeat the Great Square, as he stole a power from you, which if used, will be too powerful to defeat.
  • In this little adventure, you will:
    • Back to the classics in this arcade style
    • Kill various types of enemies
    • Jump through dangerous places
